  <chunk id="39b557ab42e265c37acee079b474c73708f197c7.c3" text="Conclusions/Significance: Our findings reveal a mechanism for uptake of metal ions in S. suis and this mechanism provides a reasonable explanation as to how SsTroA operates in metal transport. Citation: Zheng B, Zhang Q, Gao J, Han H, Li M, et al. (2011) Insight into the Interaction of Metal Ions with TroA from Streptococcus suis. PLoS ONE 6(5): e19510.">
